title: Get Your Guaranteed Taylor Swift Eras Tour Resale Tickets: Don't Miss Out on Front-Row Seats!
originSummary: The article provides information on where to find resale tickets for Taylor Swift's Eras Tour in the UK, mentioning websites viagogo and Vivid Seats.
It mentions that there are still front-row tickets available for certain shows, but they are selling quickly.
The article advises fans to wait for prices to settle before purchasing tickets and highlights the upcoming re-release of Taylor Swift's album 1989 and her "Taylor's Version" of the album.

title: Alibaba sets sights on strategic innovations for growth
originSummary: Alibaba Group Holding has identified four new business pillars for future growth, including technology-driven internet platform businesses and AI-driven technology businesses.
The company will focus on strategic-level innovation in businesses such as the online wholesale marketplace 1688 and second-hand goods trading platform Xianyu.
Despite facing competition in the domestic market, Alibaba reported 9% revenue growth in the past quarter, with strong growth in its international business and Cainiao Logistics.
